        "name": "Impaling Spike",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You conjure a spike that thrusts up from the earth beneath a target creature, potentially impaling it. The spike is made of cold iron and deals 8d6 piercing damage. The target must attempt a Reflex save.",
